guarded formula characterizing all counter-examples:
"∃ A B m #i.
  (Secret( A, B, m ) @ #i)
 ∧
  (∃ #r. (K( m ) @ #r)) ∧
  (∀ #r. (Reveal( B ) @ #r) ⇒ ⊥) ∧
  (∀ #r. (Reveal( A ) @ #r) ⇒ ⊥)"
*/
